<!--
    Admin Panel - Tutorly
    
    Purpose: Administrative dashboard for managing tutors, students, and accounts
    Features:
    - View and search all tutors with role and status management
    - View and search all students with class management
    - Create new tutor accounts with password validation
    - Responsive design with mobile sidebar
    - Real-time search and filtering
    - Confirmation modals for critical actions
    - Toast notifications for user feedback
-->
